                       <summary/>

                             <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                               <locus from="1ra" to="137va"/>
                               <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2456Tergwa#Matthew">Commentary on the Gospel of Matthew</title>
                               <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                               <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">መጽሐፈ፡ ልደቱ፡ ለኢየሱስ፡ </hi>
                                 ይቤ፡ መተርጕም፡ እስመ፡ የሐትቱ፡ መተርጕማን፡ በእንተ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ክፍል፡ ሐተታ፡ ብዙኃ፨
                                </incipit>
                               <explicit xml:lang="gez">ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ አንሰ፡ ነዳይ፡ ነበብኩ፡ በእንተ፡ ፍቅር፡ መንፈሳዊት፡ ክርስቶሳዊት፡ ሥርዓተ፡ ተግሣጽ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያናዊት፨</explicit>
                               
                               <colophon xml:id="coloph1" xml:lang="gez">
                                 
                                 <locus from="136va" to="137rb"/>
                                 ተፈጸመ፡ ብስራተ፡ ማቴዎስ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ዘጸሐፋ፡ በልሳነ፡ ዕብራውያን፡ በሀገረ፡ ፍልስጤም፨
                                 ወዘኀብሩ፡ ቦቱ፡ ፬ወንጌላውያን፨ ወይእቲ፡ ፲ወ፪ምዕራፍ፡ በሱርስት፡ ወበሮማይስጥ፡ ፷ወ፯፡ ምዕራፍ፡ 
                                 ወቃላቲሃሰ፡ ፵፻ወ፬፻፡፡፺ወ፱ቃላት፡ ሱረስታዊ፨ ወዝኬ፡ ውእቱ፡ ትርጓሜ፡ አረጋዊ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ትሩፍ፡ ገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ 
                                 <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5720JohnChr">አባ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ አፈ፡ ወርቅ፡ ምሥራቃዊ፨ </persName> ወፈለሰት፡ ዛቲ፡ እምልሳነ፡ ሱርስት፡ ኃበ፡ ልሳነ፡ አረቢ፡ በከመ፡ ዘከረ፡ ለሊሁ፨
                                 ዛቲሰ፡ ፍካሬ፡ ጽሪት፡ ወንጥፍት፡ ወፍትንት፡ እንተ፡ ይእቲ፡ ፍ<gap reason="lost" unit="chars" quantity="12"/>
                                 ዝኩር፡ እምኵሎን፡ ፍካሬያት፡ <gap reason="lost" unit="chars" quantity="5"/> ይእቲ፡ ወተጽሕፈት፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ 
                                 <date>በ፲፻ወ፫፻፳ወ፰፡</date> እምዓመተ፡ እስክንድር፡ ዮናናዊ፡ ዘስዕ<gap reason="illegible" unit="chars" quantity="3"/>
                                 ለአመተ፡ ተብነላት፡ በ<date>፬፻፡ ዓመት፨</date>
                                 <note>The colophon mentions the date 1328 according to the Era of Alexander the Greek (=1647 CE?).</note>
                               </colophon>
                                 </msItem>

                               <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                                   <locus from="138ra" to="183ra"/>
                                 <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2456Tergwa#Matthew">Commentary on the Gospel of Luke</title>
                                   <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am"/>
                                 <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ፈጣሪ፡ ሕያው፡ ነባቢ፡ ብስራተ፡ ሉቃስ፡ ሐዋ</hi>ርያ፡ ላእክ። ይቤሉቃስ፡ 
                                   ሐዋርያ፡ ክቡር፡ እስመ፡ ብዙኃን፡ እለ፡ አኀዙ፡ ይውጥኑ፡ ወይብግሩ፡ ወይምሀሩ፡                                   
                                     </incipit>
                                 <colophon xml:id="coloph2" xml:lang="gez">
                                   
                                   <locus from="182ra" to="183va"/>
                                   ተፈጸመ፡ ብስራተ፡ ሉቃስ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ትሩፍ፡ ፩እም፸ወ፪አርድእት፡ ጸሎቱ፡ ትዕቀበነ፡ <sic resp="DN">ለዓለም፡</sic> ዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                                   <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="DN"/>
                                   </colophon>
                                     
                                   </msItem>

                               <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                                   <locus from="184ra" to="228rb"/>
                                 <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2456Tergwa#John">Commentary on the Gospel of John</title>
                                   <textLang mainLang="gez" otherLangs="am"/>
                                 <incipit xml:lang="gez"><hi rend="rubric">በስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ፈጣሪ፡ ሕያው፡ ቀዳማዊ፡</hi> ዘሀሎ፡ ወይሄሉ፡  እስከ፡ ለዓለም፡
                                   <hi rend="rubric">ንወጥን፡ እንከ፡ ብስራተ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወንጌላዊ። ይ</hi>ቤ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ክቡር፡ ነባቤ፡ መለኮት፨ በቀዳሚ፡ ኮነ፡ 
                                   <hi rend="rubric">ቃል፡ ህልወ። ትርጓሜ። እስመ፡ ይትኃሠሡ፡
                                     መተር</hi>ጕማን፡ 
                                     በዝንቱ፡ ክፍል፡ ተኃሠሦተ፡ ብዙኃ።
                                     </incipit>
                                 <explicit xml:lang="gez">ወአንትሙሰ፡ ተኀዘኑ፡ ወባሕቱ፡ ይደልወኒ፡ እምትር፡ ቃለ፡ ተናገሮ፡ 
                                   በዝየ፡ በእንተ፡ ትርጓሜL ብስራተ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ ሐዋርያ፡ ቡሩክ፡ ነባቤ፡ መለኮት። ወንሕነኒ፡ ንስአሎ፡ ወናስተብቍዕ፡ እምኔሁ፡ 
                                   ለዘ፡ ያነብባ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="DN"/></explicit>
                                 
                                 <colophon xml:id="coloph3" xml:lang="gez">                                   
                                   <locus target="#228rb"/>
                                   ተፈጸመ፡ ብስራተ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ ፈጻሜ፡ ብስራት፡ 
                                   ዘነበበ፡ በልሳነ፡ ዮናናዊያን፡ በሀገረ፡ ኤፌሶን፡ 
                                   ለሊሁ፡ ፳ምዕራፍ፡ ወቃላቲሁሰ፡ ፳፻ወ፭፻፴ወ፪፡ ወባቲ፡ ተፈጸመ፡ ቃላተ፡ ወንጌላት፡<gap reason="ellipsis" resp="DN"/>
                                 </colophon>                                     
                               </msItem>
                          </msContents>

                          <physDesc>
                             <objectDesc form="Codex">
                                <supportDesc>
                                   <support>
                                      <material key="parchment">The manuscript is a palimpsest. Many of the parchment leaves are reused, and bear remains of a text 
                                        in Gǝʿǝz which was removed (washed out). The remains of the lower text can be seen on many leaves, 
                                        especially on <locus target="#87v #130"/>, but also on <locus target="#1v #2v #3 #4 #117 #119 #120 #121 #124 #126 #191 #192 #193 #194 #196 #199"/>
                                        and many others. The lower text is written in a much older hand (15th century?);  on <locus target="#117r"/>, a metropolitan Yoḥannǝs
                                        is mentioned, who might be, according to C. Conti Rossini, the 15th-century <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10382Yohanne">Metropolitan Yoḥannǝs, the author of 
                                          the Homily in honour of Garimā</persName>.                                         
                                      </material>
                                   </support>
                                   <extent>
                    
                                       <measure unit="leaf" quantity="228">228</measure>
                                     <measure unit="leaf" type="blank"><locus target="#137r #137v #183v #228v"/>
                                     </measure>
