                                <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                                       <seg type="script">Second half of the 16th/first half of the 17th century script.</seg>
                                       <seg type="ink">Black, red.</seg>
                                      <desc>Fine, careful and regular; by a good scribe who wrote in small script. 
                                        It cannot be excluded that more than one scribe participated in copying. 
